    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS system overhaul to ensure timing precision. With communicative hydraulic steering and a balanced multi-link rear suspension, this vehicle offers the visceral, analog performance modern sports cars lack. Mechanically robust and ready for the apex.",
